# Runtime artifacts of plan-folder runs (the committed parts of a plan folder are
# guardrails.json, tasks/**, and state/seed.json — everything the harness writes
# at runtime is ignored). docs/, .claude/, and examples/ sources stay tracked.
**/state/state.json
**/state/run.json
**/state/logs/
**/state/merge-conflicts.log
**/state/captured/
examples/**/out/
